## 📱 Mobile Keyboard Interaction Layout (iOS / Android)

Built to maximize touch real estate using a highly intuitive **Long-Press (Hold)** pop-up strategy based on standard Latin base character keys.

[A] ──>  [ ä ] [ aa ] [ ää ]
[E] ──>  [ e ] [ ee ] [ ə ] [ əə ]
[O] ──>  [ ö ] [ öö ] [ õ ]
[U] ──>  [ ü ] [ üü ]
[L] ──>  [ ĺ ] [ l̥ ][ ĺ̥ ] [ ł ] [ ł́ ]
[R] ──>  [ ŕ ] [ r̥ ]  [ ŕ̥ ]
[N] ──>  [ ń ] [ n̥ ]  [ ń̥ ]
